        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\n!define RECTANGLE class\nskinparam componentStyle rectangle\nskinparam backgroundColor white\nskinparam arrowColor DimGray\n\ntitle Архитектурна диаграма на контейнерите (C4 Level 2)\n\nactor \&quot;Потребител\&quot; as User\n\npackage \&quot;EcoProject System\&quot; {\n    component \&quot;Frontend Application\\n[React, TypeScript, Vite]\&quot; as UI &lt;&lt;Container&gt;&gt;\n    component \&quot;Backend API Service\\n[.NET 8/Core, C#]\&quot; as API &lt;&lt;Container&gt;&gt;\n    \n    database \&quot;User Database\\n[MS SQL Server]\&quot; as SQL &lt;&lt;Container&gt;&gt;\n    file \&quot;Eco Trails Data\\n[eco.json]\&quot; as JSON &lt;&lt;Container&gt;&gt;\n}\n\ncloud \&quot;Външни AI Услуги\&quot; {\n    component \&quot;Gemini API\&quot; as Gemini &lt;&lt;External System&gt;&gt;\n    component \&quot;OpenAI API\&quot; as OpenAI &lt;&lt;External System&gt;&gt;\n}\n\n&#39; Връзки\nUser --&gt; UI : \&quot;Разглежда пътеки,\\nпише съобщения\\n[HTTPS]\&quot;\nUI --&gt; API : \&quot;Изпраща API заявки\\n[JSON/REST]\&quot;\nAPI --&gt; SQL : \&quot;Чете/Записва потребители\\nи любими пътеки\\n[EF Core / SQL]\&quot;\nAPI --&gt; JSON : \&quot;Хибридно търсене на\\nданни за маршрути\\n[File I/O]\&quot;\n\nAPI --&gt; Gemini : \&quot;Генерира отговори\\n(Основен модел)\\n[HTTPS/gRPC]\&quot;\nAPI --&gt; OpenAI : \&quot;Генерира отговори\\n(Резервен модел - Fallback)\\n[HTTPS]\&quot;\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="T40RJ8XfpmUU6eO2Z14V-1">
